side-effects:
Side-effects see notes above; also gastro-intestinal disturbances;
chest pain; influenza-like symptoms including pharyngitis and sinusitis;
urinary-tract infection; arthralgia, myalgia, back pain, leg cramps;
eczema; less commonly dry mouth, flatulence, anxiety,
vertigo, tendinitis-like symptoms, abnormal vision, increased sweating; rarely bradycardia, tachycardia, dyspnoea, insomnia, depression,
blood disorders, increase in uric acid, eosinophilia, rash, and pruritus;
syncope and asthenia also reported

